The YAW platform consist of 2 components:

1. The embeddable YAW container
  - Google AuthSub authentication to YouTube
  - Direct video upload to YouTube

2. The YAW admin panel
  - Manage assignments
  - Manage video submissions
  - Generate embed code for YAW container for each assignment
  - Preview submitted videos
  - Search filter for assigments and submissions
  
The project is currently available as an alpha release.
To get started, please read the Getting Started guide at

  http://code.google.com/p/yaw-project/wiki/GettingStartedGuide
  
and download the latest release at

  http://code.google.com/p/yaw-project/downloads/list